  - Use GNetworkMonitor to monitor network changes (#664096)
  - Remove use of deprecated GTK+ APIs (#664120)
  - Fix icon in PDM's "Clear All" button (#663159)
  - Show the WebKit version in the about dialog
  - Other  minor fixes

